                    <li><strong>Verb in URL:</strong> The path <code>/createUser</code> includes the verb "createUser."</li>
                    <li><strong>Data in Query Parameters:</strong> Passing data for creation in query parameters is less secure, less flexible, and not suitable for complex data structures compared to sending data in the request body, which is standard for <code>POST</code> requests.</li>
