            <h4>Design Problems:</h4>
            <ul class="problem-list">
                <li><strong>Incorrect HTTP Method:</strong> "GET" is for retrieving data and should be idempotent and safe. Creating a resource changes state and should use "POST".</li>
                <li><strong>Verb in URI:</strong> "createUser" is a verb. URIs identify resources.</li>
                <li><strong>Query Parameters for Creation:</strong> Sending creation data via query parameters is generally discouraged for several reasons:
